---
import DashboardLayout from "../layouts/DashboardLayout.astro";
import Icon from "../components/Icon.astro";
---

<DashboardLayout>
	<div class="hero">
		<p class="intro">
			RadSafety는 <strong>대한핵의학회 방사선안전위원회</strong>와 <strong
				>대한핵의학기술학회 안전관리위원회</strong
			>가 회원들과 유용한 정보를 공유하기 위해 개발 중인 앱입니다.
		</p>

		<div class="card-grid">
			<a href="/inspection-prep" class="card primary">
				<div class="card-header">
					<Icon name="check-square" size="20" class="card-icon" />
					<h3>정기검사 수검준비</h3>
				</div>
				<p class="card-desc">
					KINS 정기검사 수검가이드 및 실무 체크리스트
				</p>
			</a>

			<a href="/findings-recommendations" class="card secondary">
				<div class="card-header">
					<Icon name="alert-circle" size="20" class="card-icon" />
					<h3>지적권고사례</h3>
				</div>
				<p class="card-desc">정기검사 지적 및 권고 사례 모음</p>
			</a>

			<a href="/resources" class="card secondary">
				<div class="card-header">
					<Icon name="folder" size="20" class="card-icon" />
					<h3>자료실</h3>
				</div>
				<p class="card-desc">작성지침, 예시 및 각종 발표자료</p>
			</a>

			<a href="mailto:kimbi.kirams@gmail.com" class="card secondary">
				<div class="card-header">
					<Icon name="mail" size="20" class="card-icon" />
					<h3>의견문의</h3>
				</div>
				<p class="card-desc">
					kimbi.kirams@gmail.com으로 연락 부탁드립니다. (앱내 의견
					전송 기능 개발 예정)
				</p>
			</a>
		</div>

		<!-- Action Area -->
		<div
			style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"
		>
			<a
				href="/login"
				style="
				display: inline-block;
				background-color: var(--accent);
				color: white;
				padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 99px;
				font-weight: bold;
				text-decoration: none;
				font-size: 0.95rem;
				box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
				transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
			"
				class="primary-cta-btn"
			>
				카카오 또는 이메일 인증으로 앱 시작하기
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>

	<style>
		.hero {
			text-align: left;
			padding: 0; /* Minimized */
			max-width: 800px;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}
		h1 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
			margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			color: #111827;
		}
		.intro {
			font-size: 0.85rem;
			color: #6b7280;
			margin: 0 0 1rem 0; /* Minimized */
			line-height: 1.4;
		}
		.card-grid {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
			gap: 0.4rem; /* Ultra Tight Gap */
			text-align: left;
		}
		.card {
			padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem; /* Smoothed Padding */
			border-radius: 8px;
			box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px var(--shadow-color);
			text-decoration: none;
			color: inherit;
			transition:
				transform 0.2s,
				box-shadow 0.2s;
			border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
		}
		.card:hover {
			transform: translateY(-4px);
			box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px var(--shadow-color);
			background-color: #27272a !important; /* Slightly lighter on hover */
		}
		.card.primary {
			border-left: 5px solid var(--accent);
		}

		.primary-cta-btn:hover {
			transform: scale(1.05);
			box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5);
		}

		.card-header {
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			gap: 0.4rem;
			margin-bottom: 0.2rem; /* Tight header margin */
		}

		/* Pass class via global styles or explicit prop if component supports it. 
		   Since Icon.astro applies {className}, usage <Icon class="card-icon" /> works.
		*/
		:global(.card-icon) {
			color: var(--text-muted);
		}

		.card h3 {
			margin: 0;
			color: var(--text-main);
			font-size: 1rem;
			font-weight: 600;
		}
		.card p.card-desc {
			margin: 0;
			font-size: 0.8rem;
			color: var(--text-muted);
			line-height: 1.3;
		}

		@media (max-width: 480px) {
			.card p.card-desc {
				font-size: 0.75rem; /* Slightly smaller on small screens */
			}
			.card-header h3 {
				font-size: 0.95rem;
			}
		}

		@media (max-width: 768px) {
			.desktop-only {
				display: none;
			}
		}
		@media (min-width: 769px) {
			.mobile-only {
				display: none;
			}
		}
	</style>
</DashboardLayout>
